{
  "texts": [
    "This paper employs a composite method that includes CNNs in combination with DWT and SVM 17.",
    "To address the difficulties in diagnosing colorectal cancer, this system incorporates the most advanced feature extraction, classification, and segmentation techniques.",
    "Additionally, the proposed PolynetDWTCADx can achieve average detection accuracy for malignant tissues and comprehensive segmentation for precise treatment planning through the CKHK-22 dataset.",
    "As a step-in computer-assisted diagnosis, this state-of-theart CADx system enhances the potential of identifying colorectal cancer at an early stage with high accuracy.",
    "Comprehensive block diagram of PolynetDWTCADx."
  ]
}